        "id": "tool_write_message_to_human_eiD3ZxiILNGnluQ0sbl7",
        "type": "function",
        "function": {
          "name": "write_message_to_human",
          "arguments": "{\"text\": \"If ignoring her helps you maintain your own space and energy, then do it. It's not 'rage-quitting' life; it's protecting your own resources. It's the same principle of focus: don't let the noise drain you if you have a goal to work towards. What's more important to you: showing your frustration, or getting your project done and eventually moving out? If the latter is the goal, then maybe 'ignoring' is the most practical, 'pro-player' move you can make. What do you think?\"}"
